**Godot:** `14-godot-mobile-performance.mdc`.

Mobile performance rules:

- Target stable 60 FPS on mid-range mobile when possible.
- Pool enemies, projectiles, VFX, damage numbers, and UI popups.
- Avoid per-frame LINQ in gameplay.
- Avoid Instantiate/Destroy during active waves except early prototype.
- Avoid GetComponent calls in combat loops.
- Prefer squared distance checks for ranges.
- Keep VFX restrained; do not flood the screen.
